title: Hizamazuite Ai O Tou
alternative_title: 跪いて愛を問う ; On My Knees, Asking for Love
status: 跪いて愛を問う ; On My Knees, Asking for Love
description:
Description :
        Being “dominated” and rejoicing... A world where there are Doms who want to dominate people, Subs who want to be ruled, and people who have a second gender. In order to make a living, Masami works as a cast member at a club dedicated to Sub, and at the moment he is pointed out as a Sub by a transfer student, Yuu, and given an order...!?
